text: The Alantaya Taungdan"Alantaya Taungdan (Approved)" , United States National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (Alantaya Range; ) is a range of mountains or hills in Kayin State, in the southern part of the Burma (Myanmar).Burma 1:250,000 topographic map, Series U542, ND 47-02 Ye U.S. Army Map Service, December 1959 It is part of the Tenasserim Range. ==See also== *Tenasserim Hills ==Notes== Category:Mountain ranges of Myanmar
title: Alantaya Taungdan
